def fftpeaks(sig):
    yf = fft(sig)
    xf = fftfreq(len(sig))
    s = slice(1, len(xf)//2)
    idx = np.argmax(np.abs(yf[s]))
    freq = xf[s][idx]
    phase = np.angle(yf[s][idx])/2/np.pi/freq
    return 1/freq*np.arange(9) - phase
